{"lemma":"بَنَفْسَجاتٌ","slug":"بَنَفْسَجاتٌ","root":"NTWS","root_slug":"NTWS","root_link":"/words/roots/NTWS","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n3331"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8E%D9%86%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%92%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%AC%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"violet","tags":["collective"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Middle Iranian; see بنفشه (banafše) and compare Middle Persian wnpšk' (wanafšag, “violet”)."},"ipa":["/ba.naf.sad͡ʒ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n3331","headword_ar":"بَنَفْسَجٌ","root":"bnfsj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEal~alN","text_ar":"قَعَلَّلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safarojalN","text_ar":"سَفَرْجَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) [an arabicized word, from the Persian"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"banafo$a","text_ar":"بَنَفْشَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"violet; viola odorata"},{"kind":"text","text":"of Linn: and accord. to Forskål (Flora AEgypt. Arab. p. ciii.) applied in El-Yemen to the “"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"iris:"},{"kind":"text","text":"” and (p. cxx.) “"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tagetes dubia?"},{"kind":"text","text":"”] what is thus called is well known:"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the smelling it in its fresh state is beneficial to those who are heated by wrath"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaHoruwriyn","text_ar":"المَحْرُورِين"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the continual smelling of it induces good sleep: the conserve made of it is beneficial for the pleurisy"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAtu Aljanobi","text_ar":"ذَاتُ الجَنْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and for inflammation of the lungs"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAtu Alr~iy^api","text_ar":"ذَاتُ الرِّيَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and for cough, and for headache."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}